messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Security Report

Thanks to the tireless efforts of our security and intelligence divisions, there are currently no credible threats to Black Festive Airstrip 65. All station construction projects have been authorized. Have a secure shift!

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Power Systems Nominal

All SMESs on Black Festive Airstrip 65 have been recharged. We apologize for the inconvenience.

messages.author: Central Command
messages.body:
Power Systems Nominal

Power has been restored to Black Festive Airstrip 65. We apologize for the inconvenience.
